        <mxCell id="22" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;align=left;spacingLeft=6;" value="1) Assessment is append-only; versions are never overwritten.&#xa;2) Preliminary assessments may have null filing_id.&#xa;3) Exactly one active policy record per taxpayer/policy type at a point in time.&#xa;4) Filing totals must be reproducible from LineFact records.&#xa;5) Claim dispatch uses idempotency_key for safe retries.&#xa;6) All cross-service decisions must be traceable via trace_id." vertex="1">
